NAME
    Pod::Weaver::PluginBundle::Author::PERLANCAR - PERLANCAR's default
    Pod::Weaver config

VERSION
    This document describes version 0.290 of
    Pod::Weaver::PluginBundle::Author::PERLANCAR (from Perl distribution
    Pod-Weaver-PluginBundle-Author-PERLANCAR), released on 2021-06-04.

SYNOPSIS
    In "weaver.ini":

     [@Author::PERLANCAR]

    or in "dist.ini":

     [PodWeaver]
     config_plugin = @Author::PERLANCAR

DESCRIPTION
    Equivalent to (see source code).

